He’s so content just having me near and it’s the best feeling in the world. It’s no wonder my mama had 11 of us, I’m certain she couldn’t get enough of this newborn season ☺️. #cedricmikula #1month
the joy of feeling better after an icky two weeks of taking turns with the stomach bug for the 2nd round this season. #vscocam #mikulasiblings

18 months apart isn’t the easiest at first, both in diapers, both not able to express themselves, different nap schedules, different food schedules etc etc. But fast forward a couple years and it truly is the best thing ever. Now to time our 4th and possibly last to make sure Cédric has a pal to grow up and play with too. 
#mikulasiblings #vscocam

our family turned 11 years old yesterday and it also happens to be the first anniversary we’re apart. He’s sick in FL tending to grandpa after we got a call he might not have much time left and we need to look into getting him home. And I’m home sick with three sick kids. To say this year has been a whirlwind would be an understatement, so many highs and yet hard lows, but no matter what life throws at us or what goals we’ve set in place that are challenging us right now I couldn’t have dreamed of a better partner, husband, best friend & father. Love is: how he never leaves for work before making sure all the baby bottles are washed and water boiled in case I need to get up and make a bottle early in the morning. 😭 I’m especially sappy today because he’s away lol Happy 11th @thebarberscut we love you so much, hurry home. ♥️
These colds for 3 out of the 5 of us are lasting way too long, we’re so over it.
